        <link rel="schema.DC" href="https://purl.org/DC/elements/1.0/" /><meta name="citation_journal_title" content="RadioGraphics" /><meta name="dc.Title" content="Radionuclide Imaging of Cardiac Amyloidosis and Sarcoidosis: Roles                    and Characteristics of Various Tracers" /><meta name="dc.Creator" content="Masatoshi  Hotta" /><meta name="dc.Creator" content="Ryogo  Minamimoto" /><meta name="dc.Creator" content="Toru  Awaya" /><meta name="dc.Creator" content="Michiaki  Hiroe" /><meta name="dc.Creator" content="Osamu  Okazaki" /><meta name="dc.Creator" content="Yukio  Hiroi" /><meta name="dc.Description" content="Radionuclide imaging with use of bone tracers and PET amyloid agents is a powerful tool that yields high sensitivity for diagnosis of cardiac amyloidosis and sarcoidosis." /><meta name="Description" content="Radionuclide imaging with use of bone tracers and PET amyloid agents is a powerful tool that yields high sensitivity for diagnosis of cardiac amyloidosis and sarcoidosis." /><meta name="dc.Description" content="Amyloidosis and sarcoidosis are systemic diseases that affect multiple organ systems. Accurate diagnosis of cardiac amyloidosis and sarcoidosis is particularly important because cardiac involvement..." /><meta name="Description" content="Amyloidosis and sarcoidosis are systemic diseases that affect multiple organ systems. Accurate diagnosis of cardiac amyloidosis and sarcoidosis is particularly important because cardiac involvement..." /><meta name="dc.Publisher" content=" Radiological Society of North America " /><meta name="dc.Date" scheme="WTN8601" content="2020-09-25" /><meta name="dc.Type" content="research-article" /><meta name="dc.Format" content="text/HTML" /><meta name="dc.Identifier" scheme="manuscript" content="200068" /><meta name="dc.Identifier" scheme="doi" content="10.1148/rg.2020200068" /><meta name="dc.Identifier" scheme="url" content="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.2020200068" /><meta name="dc.Source" content="https